Teprotumumab Efficacy, Safety, and Durability in Longer-Duration Thyroid Eye 
Disease and Re-treatment: OPTIC-X Study.

Douglas RS(1), Kahaly GJ(2), Ugradar S(3), Elflein H(4), Ponto KA(5), Fowler 
BT(6), Dailey R(7), Harris GJ(8), Schiffman J(9), Tang R(9), Wester S(10), Jain 
AP(11), Marcocci C(12), Marinò M(12), Antonelli A(13), Eckstein A(14), 
